<varlistentry id="options.DecorateTransients">
	<term>DecorateTransients</term>
	<listitem>
		<para> Specifies  that  transient  windows (pop-up dialog boxes), which
		are normally not decorated, should be given the usual title  and
		low  bars.   Note: some pop-up windows and menus are not managed
		by the window manager, so do not get these decorations.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
